   "source": [
    "# Quality score of raw reads"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import os\n",
    "import itertools as it\n",
    "import toolz as tz\n",
    "import toolz.curried as c\n",
    "\n",
    "from fun_fastq import stream_fastq\n",
    "\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "plt.style.use('seaborn-whitegrid')\n",
    "\n",
    "DIR_DAT_RAW  = \"/home/jovyan/work/Data/SRR4841864/rawdata\"\n",
    "DIR_DAT_TRIM = \"/home/jovyan/work/Data/SRR4841864/trimmed_fastqs/\"\n",
    "DIR_CUR      = \"/home/jovyan/work/GitRepo/Duke_CBB520_HW2\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Visualization of Phred scores for all bases"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1080x432 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fn   = \"SRR4841864_1.fastq\"          # file name\n",
    "fp   = os.path.join(DIR_DAT_RAW, fn) # file path\n",
    "gen1 = stream_fastq(fp)              # generator\n",
    "\n",
    "fn   = \"SRR4841864_2.fastq\"          # file name\n",
    "fp   = os.path.join(DIR_DAT_RAW, fn) # file path\n",
    "gen2 = stream_fastq(fp)              # generator\n",
    "\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(ncols=2, nrows=1, figsize=(15, 6))\n",
    "for cnt, reads in enumerate(zip(gen1, gen2)):\n",
    "    for ax, read in zip(axes, reads):\n",
    "        qscore  = read[\"qscore\"]\n",
    "        phred   = [ord(char)-33 for char in qscore]\n",
    "        ax.plot(phred, alpha = 0.3)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if cnt > 100:\n",
    "        break\n",
    "\n",
    "### Set plot axes\n",
    "ax1, ax2 = axes\n",
    "ax1.set_title(\"SRR4841864_1.fastq\")\n",
    "ax2.set_title(\"SRR4841864_2.fastq\")\n",
    "\n",
    "ax1.set_ylim([0, 42])\n",
    "ax2.set_ylim([0, 42])\n",
    "\n",
    "ax1.set_xlabel(\"Index of Bases\")\n",
    "ax2.set_xlabel(\"Index of Bases\")\n",
    "\n",
    "ax1.set_ylabel(\"Phred Score\")\n",
    "ax2.set_ylabel(\"Phred Score\")\n",
    "pass"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Visualization Phred scores using boxplot"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1440x720 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "### stream the files\n",
    "fn   = \"SRR4841864_1.fastq\"          # file name\n",
    "fp   = os.path.join(DIR_DAT_RAW, fn) # file path\n",
    "gen1 = stream_fastq(fp)              # generator\n",
    "\n",
    "fn   = \"SRR4841864_2.fastq\"          # file name\n",
    "fp   = os.path.join(DIR_DAT_RAW, fn) # file path\n",
    "gen2 = stream_fastq(fp)              # generator\n",
    "\n",
    "N = 100\n",
    "\n",
    "### convert to phred score\n",
    "reads = tz.pipe(\n",
    "    gen1,\n",
    "    c.take(N),\n",
    "    c.map(lambda x: x['qscore']),\n",
    "    c.map(list),\n",
    "    c.map(lambda x: [ord(char)-33 for char in x])\n",
    ")\n",
    "reads  = np.array(list(reads))\n",
    "reads1 = list(reads.T)\n",
    "\n",
    "reads = tz.pipe(\n",
    "    gen2,\n",
    "    c.take(N),\n",
    "    c.map(lambda x: x['qscore']),\n",
    "    c.map(list),\n",
    "    c.map(lambda x: [ord(char)-33 for char in x])\n",
    ")\n",
    "reads  = np.array(list(reads))\n",
    "reads2 = list(reads.T)\n",
    "\n",
    "### generate boxplot\n",
    "fig, (ax1, ax2) = plt.subplots(ncols=1, nrows=2, figsize=(20, 10))\n",
    "ax1.boxplot(reads1)\n",
    "ax2.boxplot(reads2)\n",
    "\n",
    "ax1.set_title(\"SRR4841864_1.fastq\")\n",
    "ax2.set_title(\"SRR4841864_2.fastq\")\n",
    "ax1.set_xlabel(\"Index of Bases\")\n",
    "ax2.set_xlabel(\"Index of Bases\")\n",
    "ax1.set_ylabel(\"Phred\")\n",
    "ax2.set_ylabel(\"Phred\")\n",
    "pass"
   ]
  }
 ],
